as in personal possession a loaded firearm while intoxicated; is guilty of a Class 1 misdemeanor. Section 2. That chapter 22-14 be amended with a NEW SECTION: A person is guilty of a Class 1 misdemeanor if the person is in personal possession of a loaded firearm while: (1) Intoxicated; or (2) Under the influence of marijuana, as that term is defined in \u00a7 22-42-1. Section 3. That chapter 22-14 be amended with a NEW SECTION: For purposes of section 2 of this Act, the term, loaded firearm, means any firearm that contains a cartridge, shell, or projectile: (1) In the chamber, including any chamber in the cylinder of a revolver; (2) In a magazine that is fixed or integral to the firearm; or (3) In a detachable magazine that has been inserted into the firearm."}], "amendments": [{"bill_id": 22758, "document_id": 231547, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/231547.pdf", "legislator_profile_id": 3954, "document_id_instructions": 231549, "document_id_instructions_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/231549.pdf"}, {"bill_id": 22758, "document_id": 233456, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/233456.pdf", "legislator_profile_id": 3954, "document_id_instructions": 233494, "document_id_instructions_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/233494.pdf"}], "fiscal_notes": [], "action_log": [{"bill_id": 22758, "action_date": "2022-01-13T13:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 226915, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/226915.pdf", "status_text": "First read in House and referred to", "journal_page": 24, "committee_id_action": 1008, "committee_id_assigned": 1009, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 22758, "action_date": "2022-01-21T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 228114, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/228114.pdf", "status_text": "Scheduled for hearing", "journal_page": 1, "committee_id_action": 1009, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N",